---
import BlogLayout from '../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
const allPosts = await Astro.glob('../pages/posts/*.md');
const pageTitle = 'My Astro Learning Blog';
---

<BlogLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
	<h1>My Astro Learning Blog</h1>
	<p>This is where I will post about my journey learning Astro.</p>
	<p>
		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Reiciendis, sed asperiores neque officia odio ullam commodi molestiae quas consectetur ipsum molestias quaerat consequatur ut aspernatur recusandae hic minus similique delectus enim accusamus accusantium aut. Odio quo tempora et optio
		repellendus soluta voluptatibus explicabo eius! Consequatur eveniet unde dolorum repellat eligendi!
	</p>
	<ul>
		{
			allPosts.map((post) => (
				<li>
					<a href={post.url}>{post.frontmatter.title}</a>
				</li>
			))
		}
	</ul>
</BlogLayout>
